overview.en: Wise Blockchain is based on the proven of history framework design (laboratory TPS 46 million times per second) to develop a high-performance backbone, based on a large number of device nodes distributed node architecture, ultra-high-capacity concurrent computing capabilities, while incorporating a number of mature cross-domain technologies, Including equipment IOT IoT technology, big data analysis, distributed cloud computing, AI artificial intelligence, etc., forming the overall framework of blockchain + big data + IOT + distributed computing + AI, using blockchain encryption algorithm to ensure fairness And intelligent terminal device operation management platform for encryption security.
overview.zh: Wise Blockchain 基于 prove of history 框架设计(实验室 TPS46 万次每 秒)开发高性能主链，基于大量设备节点的分布式的节点架构、超高容量并发计 算能力，同时融合多项成熟跨领域技术，包括设备 IOT 物联网技术，大数据分 析，分布式云计算，AI 人工智能等，形成区块链+大数据+IOT+分布式计算+AI 的整体框架，以区块链加密算法方式來保证公平性和加密安全性的智能终端设备 运营管理平台。
